thread.title: SK Hynix says Q3 profit up 6.3 pct on year, meets expecations
thread.title_full: SK Hynix says Q3 profit up 6.3 pct on year, meets expecations | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: SK Hynix says Q3 profit up 6.3 pct on year, meets expecations
text:
SEOUL Oct 22 South Korean chipmaker SK Hynix Inc said on Thursday its July-September operating profit rose 6.3 percent from a year earlier, in line with market expectations.
SK Hynix reported a profit of 1.4 trillion won ($1.23 billion), compared with 1.3 trillion won a year earlier and a 1.4 trillion won Thomson Reuters SmartEstimate derived from a poll of 16 analysts. ($1 = 1,139.1600 won) (Reporting by Se Young Lee; Editing by Stephen Coates)
